  "local_port": 47906,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are the best location to invest in Ahmedabad?",
  "response": "Investing in real estate in Ahmedabad can be a wise decision, given the city's growing economy and infrastructure development. Here are some of the best locations to consider for investment in Ahmedabad:\n\n1. **SG Highway (Sarkhej-Gandhinagar Highway)**\n   - **Why:** This area is a rapidly developing corridor with excellent connectivity to major parts of the city. It hosts numerous commercial and residential projects, making it a prime investment spot.\n   - **Pros:** High rental yields, good connectivity, and continuous development.\n\n2. **Prahlad Nagar**\n   - **Why:** Known for its upscale residential and commercial properties, Prahlad Nagar is a preferred location for affluent buyers and investors.\n   - **Pros:** Proximity to major business hubs, good schools, and hospitals.\n\n3. **Bopal and Ghuma**\n   - **Why:** These areas are seeing significant residential development and are becoming popular among middle and upper-middle-class families.\n   - **Pros:** Affordable compared to central areas, good amenities, and growing infrastructure.\n\n4. **Thaltej**\n   - **Why:** A well-established residential area with a good mix of high-rise apartments and independent houses.\n   - **Pros:** Well-developed social infrastructure, including schools, hospitals, and shopping centers.\n\n5. **Vastrapur**\n   - **Why:** Vastrapur is a sought-after location for both residential and commercial properties due to its central location and amenities.\n   - **Pros:** Proximity to the Vastrapur Lake, good connectivity, and a vibrant social scene.\n\n6. **Maninagar**\n   - **Why:** This area is undergoing redevelopment and offers more affordable options compared to other parts of the city.\n   - **Pros:** Good connectivity via public transport, and potential for appreciation due to ongoing development projects.\n\n7. **Gota**\n   - **Why:** Gota is emerging as a new residential hub with various new projects coming up.\n   - **Pros:** Affordable prices, good connectivity to SG Highway, and potential for growth.\n\nWhen investing, consider factors such as future development plans, connectivity, and the presence of essential amenities. It's also advisable to consult with local real estate experts to get the latest insights and make an informed decision.",
